Mailchimp has been the default email marketing platform for small businesses since 2001. For med spas entering 2026, the question isn't whether Mailchimp works—it's whether it works well enough for the specific demands of aesthetic medicine marketing. After testing the platform across dozens of med spa accounts and comparing it against industry-specific alternatives, our team has strong opinions on where it excels and where it falls short.

